strings:
<voice_0x01000E09><se_low>*: Hey, you guys! This is a mole's world!
But I wouldn't be nothin', nothin' without
an audience. Wanna dig my funky tune?

<voice_0x01000E0A><se_low>*: You dug it, baby!
Papa's in the swing!
Ain't it funky now? Ha!
<voice_0x01000E0B><se_low>*: Can I hit ya one more time?

<voice_0x01000E0C><se_low>*: Right on!
Dig on up! Dig on down!
Yeah, sugar!

<voice_0x01000E0D><se_low>*: Ow! Jump back!
You come to steal my harp!?
That ain't hip!

<voice_0x01000E0E><se_low>*: I'm ready to get up and do my thing!
Hit me now!
